.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Movie-Genre: western, satire, musical, spy, family
Flower: rose, amaryllis, zinnia, orchid, dahlia
Birthday: january, october, august, march, february
1. Nationality:british == Color:red
2. Nationality:swedish == Birthday:august
3. Nationality:danish == Movie-Genre:spy
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Movie-Genre:satire
6. Flower:zinnia == Birthday:october
7. Color:yellow == Flower:amaryllis
8. Movie-Genre:musical is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Flower:dahlia is on the left or right of Birthday:january
11. Birthday:februarys is on the left or right of Flower:amaryllis
12. Flower:rose == Movie-Genre:western
13. Nationality:german == Flower:orchid
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Flower:dahlia is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:family

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Birthday		|     january	|    february	|     october	|     march	|      august	|
| Movie-Genre	|    family	|     spy	|     musical	|    satire	|      western	|
| Flower		|   amaryllis	|    dahlia	|  zinnia	|    orchid	|   rose	|
